note.body:
Currently, the SSO setting is obtained from configuration like this:

```c
char const *sso_value = nm_setting_vpn_get_data_item (s_vpn, NM_FORTISSLVPN_KEY_SSO);
gboolean sso = sso_value && !strcmp(sso_value, "yes");
```

I would prefer to use `nm_setting_option_get_boolean()`, but I get warnings that it's not available before version 1.26. What is the range of NM versions this plugin needs to be compatible with?
